PLACEHOLDER: Replace this file with the real bsrnn_vocals.onnx (approx 45 MB).

To obtain:
  1. pip install torch bsrnn-pytorch
  2. python scripts/export_bsrnn_onnx.py --output public/app/models/bsrnn_vocals.onnx
     OR see: https://github.com/amanteur/BandSplitRNN-Pytorch

IMPORTANT: Delete this .placeholder file after placing the real .onnx.
Do NOT commit large binary .onnx files directly — use Git LFS:
  git lfs track '*.onnx'
  git add .gitattributes
